  dialogue:
  - What a nasy shop! Oh, at least you're not the ugliest thing in this place.
  - Anyways, will you fetch me that purple donut. It looks so stupid I want to smash
    it under my heel.
  responses:
  - responseText: I think you have issues.
    dialogueObject: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 41edb53b791621e479ca4fe35685facf, type: 2}
    customerExpression: {fileID: -1241096452, guid: 869299fc20f309045b0055679c82e76a, type: 3}
  - responseText: Are you even going to eat it?
    dialogueObject: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 184c1d721a9adf34c82b6ab10e9e6dcc, type: 2}
